ğŸ“Œ Abandon Rate (%)

ğŸ“Œ Handling Efficiency (%)

ğŸ“Œ Average ASA per Month

ğŸ“Œ Calls Handled Within Threshold

ğŸ“Œ Agent Performance Ranking

